WEBVTT

00:00:03.250 --> 00:00:06.648
(Applause)

00:00:06.748 --> 00:00:11.256
Shah Rukh Khan: To say a lot
without saying anything is not easy.

00:00:11.280 --> 00:00:16.136
It’s believed that you need a lot of maturity
and experience to be able to achieve that.

00:00:16.160 --> 00:00:20.656
But a 20-year-old college student from Delhi
University proved this thinking wrong.

00:00:20.680 --> 00:00:25.576
At such a young age,
despite so much opposition,

00:00:25.600 --> 00:00:28.016
she held her ground.

00:00:28.040 --> 00:00:32.896
She faced the barrage of hate words
with the power of her own sane ones.